thumb.title: The Doghouse, LLC
thumb.description: The Doghouse, LLC is a family-owned professional dog training business and training facility operated by Jordan and Carrie Silva Wooddell. Conveniently situated in Pinellas Park, FL, The Doghouse, LLC has been a trusted name in the St. Petersburg/Tampa Bay area since 2005. The Doghouse, LLC helps you achieve a lifelong partnership with your dog through reliable obedience. We specialize in Anxiety, Fear, Reactivity, Socialization issues, Basic and Advanced Obedience, Sport Training, Off Leash Control, and Overall Behavior Modification.The Doghouse, LLC4365 62nd Ave N, Pinellas Park, FL 33781(727) 201-9790https://thedoghousellc.com/
